    {
      "turn_id": 2,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "clarify",
      "utterance": "明白了。时间轴我用毫秒单位，格式显示为%L。两个section分别放串行和并行，每个section里画三个Request A/B/C的任务条，最后加一个milestone标记总耗时。这样结构对吗？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "axisFormat %L",
        "section Sequential",
        "section Parallel",
        "milestone"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 3,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "confirm",
      "utterance": "对，串行那边Request A从0到1000ms，B等A结束再从1000到2000ms，C继续往后。并行那边三个请求都从0开始，一起到1000ms结束。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Request A",
        "Request B",
        "Request C",
        "0, 1000ms",
        "1000, 2000ms",
        "2000, 3000ms"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 4,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "execute",
      "utterance": "好，我先画串行section：三个任务依次排开，每个1000ms，milestone落在3000ms。然后并行section三个任务都从0开始，宽度都是1000ms，milestone落在1000ms。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Sequential (HealthTech_LabAnalyzer)",
        "Parallel (HealthTech_EMR_Sync)",
        "Total: 3000ms",
        "Total: 1000ms"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 5,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "repair",
      "utterance": "等等，milestone的语法检查一下——我记得milestone后面要跟着时间点，而且你刚才说的\"3000ms\"和\"1000ms\"作为标签，但时间点本身应该是纯数字。让我确认下：串行milestone是3000, 3000ms，并行是1000, 1000ms，对吧？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "milestone, 3000, 3000ms",
        "milestone, 1000, 1000ms"
      ],
      "is_repair": true
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 6,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "confirm",
      "utterance": "是的，已经修正了。milestone的格式是\"milestone, 时间点, 标签\"，所以串行是3000位置标\"3000ms\"，并行是1000位置标\"1000ms\"。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "milestone, 3000, 3000ms",
        "milestone, 1000, 1000ms"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
